Maxima watched the tripreds as they left. Glad that now she could somewhat 
lower her defenses. 

As Hydras spoke to Perceptor, she stumbled a little. Then looked at him with 
a weak smile & nodded weakly. All she did was pat his arm gently with a weak 
squeeze then started back for the base, trudging along with barely any 
strength.
